Quick overview of the available scripts

1) source ./init.sh -- sets PREVIEWBOT_HOME in .bashrc. This needs to be done only once
2) source ./activate-virtualenv.sh -- well, activates it
3) sudo ./install-requirements.sh
4) sudo ./deploy.sh -- to be done only on the server

Internally, some of the scrips call check_init.sh to see if the environment variable is set

